title: Welcome to Jurassic League
body:
{{champion:40}} : Hi I'm Janna and today I will be your guide today. We start off by heading to the top lane. careful of the minion block, a straight line may take ages:
https://media1.giphy.com/media/HHGAwpHDiaS4/200.gif#22
{{champion:40}} :Looks like the enemy  {{champion:58}} is after our {{champion:83}} 
https://media2.giphy.com/media/rWPQnSwsKVxN6/200.gif#106
{{champion:40}} : But {{champion:83}} tries to turn it around by summoning his mist walkers. Might be a long fight.
https://media1.giphy.com/media/GVMHiDQ7AMGwU/200.gif#110

{{champion:40}} : We go to the jungle now and ---------
https://media.giphy.com/media/lYaAMHOBCWNKE/giphy.gif
 An ally has been slain{{champion:33}} 
{{champion:40}} : Top why no mia?
{{champion:83}} : Sorry

{{champion:40}} Moving on then. We now enter the mid lane and oh my! We are in for a treat, Anivia's passive has just been proced.
https://media0.giphy.com/media/eXZtqdo3tucV2/200.gif#606
{{champion:40}} :But seems like {{champion:105}}  still has his ult up
https://media4.giphy.com/media/5UWtUDnxAQaS4/200w.gif#408
An enemy has been slain{{champion:34}} 

{{champion:40}} : Finally we reach the botlane where Our {{champion:21}}  is trying to run away from the enemy {{champion:31}} 
https://media.giphy.com/media/JUXCBgvpIFfzO/giphy.gif
{{champion:21}} : OMG report noob support no help, WTF are you doing you trash noob blah blah blah blah
{{champion:40}} :  (flaming all game.......this is why I left bot)

{{champion:40}} : And now our main attraction: The aftermath of a team fight. Rip enemy{{champion:58}} {{champion:96}} {{champion:31}} 
https://media.giphy.com/media/mMcxUomlNOLVm/200.gif
{{champion:40}} :Wait....I haven't seen the enemy jungler anywhere
https://media4.giphy.com/media/l4KhRtYO4FC6qTWwM/200.gif#1
{{champion:40}} :Oh there he was........{{champion:64}}  was recalling.
